        "summary": "Appcues authenticates API requests with an API Key and API secret generated at https://studio.appcues.com/settings/keys. Supply the API Key as the username config field and the API secret as the password config field (the connector's only secret field). Both are sent together to authorize requests scoped to your account_id."
