      {
        "title": "Provide your account subdomain",
        "body": "Enter your Campayn account subdomain as the sub_domain config field. This identifies your account when the connector calls the JSON API (requests use versioned, HTTPS endpoints such as /api/v1/lists.json)."
      },
      {
        "title": "Configure and verify the connection",
        "body": "Save the connector with api_key and sub_domain set. The connector sends the key via the Authorization: TRUEREST apikey=... header against the v1 JSON API to confirm access."
      }
