        "summary": "The connector authenticates with the api_key secret field. The Meraki Dashboard API v1 accepts the key as a Bearer token via the standard HTTP Authorization header (Authorization: Bearer <api_key>). Generate the key from Organization > API & Webhooks > API keys and access; you must already be an admin in the organization. Treat the key like a password."
