        "body": "Every Metricool API call requires a userId and a blogId. Set user_id to your Metricool user ID and blog_ids to the ID(s) of the Brand(s) you want to sync. You can identify these IDs by inspecting the API endpoints used in your account (for example via the browser inspector while viewing Analytics, Planner, or Ads)."
